WEBVTT

30:06.760 --> 30:07.680 line:80%
I also heard

30:08.350 --> 30:10.040 line:80%
that in Chongzhou,
in order to collect grain,

30:10.040 --> 30:11.760 line:80%
they drove farmers to their deaths.

30:11.760 --> 30:13.440 line:80%
They all say Mr. He in our Jizhou is

30:13.440 --> 30:15.040 line:80%
a just and upright official.

30:15.040 --> 30:16.590 line:80%
I hope he won't be like those
in Chongzhou,
